<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <%- include ('../partials/head.ejs') %>
    <title>User Registration</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <header id="register-section">
        <div class="dark-overlay">
          <nav>
            <img src="uploads/logo.png" alt="">
            <div class="text-center"> 
                <a class="btn btn-warning text-white" href="/users/signin">Log in</a>
            </div>
            </nav>  
          <div class="home-inner container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-8 d-none d-lg-block">
                <h1 class="mt-5">
                  <strong>Entrepreneurs of all experience levels welcome</strong> 
                </h1>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <p>Whether you want to host a few cars to earn extra income to pay for lifeâ€™s expenses, or build a small shop with a portfolio of cars, start with one car and scale how you want.</p>
